  Vneen(A,A')/2 = Vne(A,A')/2 + Ven(A,A')/2
  V_IQA_Inter(A) = Vne(A,A')/2 + Ven(A,A')/2 + Vee(A,A')/2 + Vnn(A,A')/2
                 = VC_IQA_Inter(A) + VX_IQA_Inter(A)
                 = Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A)
                 = E_IQA_Inter(A)
  VC_IQA_Inter(A) = Vne(A,A')/2 + Ven(A,A')/2 + VeeC(A,A')/2 + Vnn(A,A')/2
                  = Coulomb Potential Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A)
                  = E_IQA_Inter(A) - VeeX(A,A')/2
  VX_IQA_Inter(A) = VeeX(A,A')/2
                  = Exchange-Correlation Energy Contribution to E_IQA_Inter(A)
                  = E_IQA_Inter(A) - VC_IQA_Inter(A)
See "2EDM Note" and "DFT Note".
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
